TextChange: Bringing happiness to others, buying materialistic things to find happiness, are all temporary. Eventually the happiness wears off, and you're left with... yourself. If you are not happy with your own self, you will not find constant happiness. Eventually the new item you bought won't be new, and will not bring as much joy.
